Building:
---------

Useful 'configure' options:
  --with-kernel-headers=DIR    path of Linux kernel headers,
                               default /usr/src/kernel-headers.

  --host=TYPE                  host platform for cross-compilation.


Building:
$ autoreconf --install
$ ./configure [--with-kernel-headers=DIR] [--host=TYPE]
$ make


Installing:
-----------

$ sudo make install


Uninstalling:
-------------

$ sudo make uninstall
